PESHAWAR, Apr 18 (APP):Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Chief Minister, Mahmood Khan here Saturday condoled the sad demise of former Chief Justice Peshawar High Court, Tariq Pervez and expressed sympathy with members of the bereaved family.
In a condolence message, the Chief Minister prayed Allah Almighty to may rest the departed soul in eternal peace and grant courage to members of the bereaved family to bear this irreparable loss with patience.
